{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0003","text":"曾給你馴服到 就像綿羊","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["過去","關係","順從"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["馴服","綿羊"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,5,0,2,4,2,2,0,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cang4","kap1","nei5","seon4","fuk6","dou3","zau6","zoeng6","min4","joeng4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"曾","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"給","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"馴服","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"PART"},{"text":"就","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"綿羊","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"回憶過去的關係狀態，用比喻「綿羊」形容順從，語氣平淡。"},"source":{"title":"好心分手","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_293","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0004","text":"何解會反咬你一下 你知嗎","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["轉變","背叛","關係破裂"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["反咬","知嗎"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,9,5,5,3,2,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ho4","gaai2","faan2","ngaau5","nei5","jat1","haa6","nei5","zi1","maa1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"何解","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"反咬","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"一下","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"知","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"嗎","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"對比過去的順從，質疑為何會突然反抗，語氣帶有不解與責備。"},"source":{"title":"好心分手","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_293","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
