{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0008","text":"沒有心 別再拖","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["結束","放手","果斷"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["沒有心","別再拖"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,2,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mut6","jau5","sam1","bit6","zoi3","to1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"沒有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"別","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"拖","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"直接表達沒有心意，要求停止拖延，語氣堅決。"},"source":{"title":"好心分手","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_293","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0009","text":"好心一早放開我 重頭努力也坎坷","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["放手","痛苦","未來艱難"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["好心","放開","坎坷"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,3,9,4,3,5,0,5,2,5,9,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hou2","sam1","jat1","zou2","fong3","hoi1","ngo5","tau4","nou5","lik6","jaa5","ham2","ho2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"好心","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"一早","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"放開","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"重頭","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"努力","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"坎坷","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"以「好心」為由要求放手，並預言重頭再來會很艱難，語氣帶有決絕。"},"source":{"title":"好心分手","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_293","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0010","text":"統統不要好過 來年歲月那麼多","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["結束","未來","時間"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["不要好過","歲月"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,9,3,4,9,4,0,0,4,2,5,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["tung2","tung2","bat1","jiu3","hou2","gwo3","loi4","nin4","seoi3","jyut6","naa5","mo1","do1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"統統","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"不要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"好過","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"來","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"年","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"歲月","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"那麼","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"多","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"認為繼續下去不會更好，並提及未來時間還很長，語氣帶有放棄。"},"source":{"title":"好心分手","artists":["盧巧音"],"lyricists":["黃偉文"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_293","prev_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_5Y2i5ben6Z-z_Mjkz_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
